@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Start resume analysis — returns job_id
# @name start_resume_analysis
POST {{baseUrl}}/resume/analyze
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----restclient

------restclient
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resume"; filename="CNPJ MEI.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ../../assets/CNPJ MEI.pdf
------restclient--

@job_id = {{start_resume_analysis.response.body.job_id}}

### Poll job status (replace with job_id from POST response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/resume/analyze/{{job_id}}
